title: Best Advice for 2019 Weightloss

description:

https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Want to lose weight in 2019? I lost 100lbs and today we talk about things you need to know to do it. These are the real things. I asked my Tribe what I should tell you and I go rapid fire on the best advice I can give you. We discuss fear of losing weight, worrying about making mistakes, why being scared of potatoes is worthless and more. Buckle up. It's a good one.
